1. MANUAL INSTALLATION

Fox Unix:
* Copy the content of the 'syntax' folder into $HOME/vimfiles/syntax
* Copy the content of the 'ftdetect' folder into $HOME/vimfiles/ftdetect

Fox Windows:
* Copy the content of the 'syntax' folder into C:\Document and Settings\User\.vim\syntax
* Copy the content of the 'ftdetect' folder into C:\Document and Settings\User\.vim\ftdetect
